This paper is about neural architecture search for image classification, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also introduces a novel hierarchical genetic representation scheme, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper discusses the design of complex topologies, which could be relevant to the field of computer architecture (cs.AR).
